</emphasis>
(
<figureCitation box="[711,773,295,320]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–8" captionStartId="6.[151,264,1887,1910]" captionTargetBox="[163,1402,195,1857]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[163,1427,195,1870]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURES 1–8. Lophilema spp.: adults. 1, L. mbulu, holotype male, Tanzania, Mbulu Mts. (ANHRT); 2, L. mbulu, paratype female, Tanzania, Mbulu Mts. (ANHRT); 3, L. bilobata, holotype male, Kenya, Aberdare Range (ZMB); 4, L. claudei, holotype male, Cameroon (ZSM); 5, L. nguru, holotype male, Tanzania, Nguru Mts. (ANHRT); 6, L. nguru, paratype male, Tanzania, Nguru Mts. (ANHRT); 7, L. curva, holotype male, Tanzania, Nguru Mts. (ANHRT); 8, L. curva, holotype male, Tanzania, Nguru Mts. (ANHRT)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2617743/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="119">Fig 3</figureCitation>
